.DT
temperature
Discworld player help
temperature

.SH Name
.SI 5
temperature - show how much warmth or cooling your items give
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
temperature
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Goes through all the items in your inventory and shows the temperature
change they give to you, heating and cooling properties.  As well as
showing your current temperature and if you are heating up or cooling.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> temperature
It's warm here.
Your yellow High Lord T-Shirt provides some warmth.
Your pair of velvet knickers provide a bit of warmth.
Your trendy skirt provides some warmth.
On balance, you are quite comfortable and are warming up slowly.
.EI
